law.catch_line: Transmittal Of Fines To State Treasurer
law.text: [ Text of section added by 2011, 178, Sec. 23 effective February 19, 2012.] The court shall transmit fines collected pursuant to sections 50 and 51 to the state treasurer. The treasurer shall deposit such fines into the Victims of Human Trafficking Trust Fund established in section 66A of chapter 10.
